properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 25 at 5:11AM AKST until January 26 at 9:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 4 to 6
inches. Winds gusting as high as 40 mph.

* WHERE...Cape Fairweather to Cape Suckling Coastal Area.

* WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to 9 AM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Heavy wet snow will
be difficult to manage.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM THIS EVENING TO 9 AM AKST SUNDAY FOR THE NORTHEAST GULF COAST
